            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5 ears corn husked (about 3 cups of kernels)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Method"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Grill the corn (10 min): Preheat your grill or grill pan to medium-high heat. Brush the corn all over with olive oil or melted butter. Grill for 2–3 minutes per side, turning occasionally, until lightly charred and tender. Set aside to cool slightly."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5 ears corn,1-2 Tablespoons olive oil"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Make the dressing (5 min): In a medium bowl, whisk together the mayo, sour cream, grated garlic, lime zest and juice, chili powder, and salt until smooth."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1/4 cup mayonnaise,1/4 cup sour cream,1 clove garlic,1 lime,1/4 teaspoon chili powder,1 teaspoon kosher salt"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Cut and mix (5 min): Slice the kernels off the cooled corn and place them in a large mixing bowl. Add the cheese, scallions, cilantro, and jalapeño. Pour the dressing over top and toss well to coat."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2 oz cotija cheese,1/3 cup finely sliced scallions,1/3 cup finely chopped cilantro,1 jalapeño pepper"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Finish and serve: Taste and adjust seasoning with more salt or lime, if needed. Garnish with extra cilantro and cheese. Serve warm, at room temp, or chilled."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Vanessa’s Quiche"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
